      ("devices", "Your tailnet devices (status / serve / ping), over the `tailscale` CLI", [], Devices.execute, Devices.help, Devices.complete)
      // CLEANUP(instances-command): `sync` currently mixes the VERB (sync now) with instance MANAGEMENT
      // (connect / disconnect / status / fetch). Those belong in a dedicated `instances` command with
      // subcommands — `instances add <url>` / `remove <name|url>` / `list` / `rename <name>` (the `--as`
      // custom-name idea) — so `dark sync` is just "pull now" and the instance list has one clear home. It
